models.name: Generative AI
models.description: The continued development owing to the expectation of higher funds is expected in Generative AI. Providing mainstream applications in generating text, videos, images, and speech mimicking humans, the generative AI is user-friendly and hence holds maximized acceptance and usage among the general masses. The next approach and research will be its effortless integration and embedding with different platforms. Besides, it also provides quantitative and qualitative growth to businesses. The generative AI has been much applauded by mainstream media as well.

models.name: Multimodal AI
models.description: AI is capable of combining numeric text, data, images, and videos for accuracy in outcomes. It enhances the performance of applications, making them more aware of context and improving their capabilities. A few benefits responsible for its trending usage are better user interaction through applications like virtual assistants and combining text, visual, and speech inputs. Cross-modal learning and enhanced creativity and innovation are other beneficial factors for the growth of multimodal AI.

models.name: Edge Computing
models.description: It is seen in distributed computing frameworks. Adding to the processing speed, it functions by increasing the proximity of data sources. Edge computing allows real-time local processing of data whose effective contribution is seen to reduce the bandwidth and latency. The reduced components play a crucial role in transferring data to a centralized location for processing. The edge computing functionalities are seen in Google Cloud platforms, ADLINKS, and others to ease remote workspace facilities.

models.name: Deep Learning
models.description: Mimicking the human brain for performing tasks has been highly fruitful in dealing with complex data. It is gaining popularity exponentially due to the presence of multiple processing layers that contribute to the accuracy of the model. The common applications are seen in product development by businesses such as autonomous driving cars, OTT platforms, customized experiences of e-commerce platforms, and others.

models.name: Explainable AI
models.description: The enhanced dependency on AI has led humans to witness higher accuracy. However, frequently, the reason and transparency behind the judgment hold more value for reliability in AI and decision-making in humans. Explainable AI bridges this gap between humans and AI by providing the set of methods or processes followed by AI to reach a specific conclusion. The interpretability to further enhance decision-making accuracy will be more prominent in the coming times in industries like healthcare, human resources, and others.

models.name: No-code Machine Learning
models.description: The no-code machine learning programs allow the use of a simple drag-and-drop interface for model building and deployment. It reduces or eliminates the need for long programming hours and code editing. The approach is more time and cost-efficient while offering speed and flexibility. It also does not require high technical expertise, thus eliminating long hours and efforts of HR.

models.name: N shot learning
models.description: It refers to enhanced techniques that allow obtaining output with minimum quantity and quality of inputs. These techniques use limited data for desired output, thus eliminating access to databases or lengthy prompts. The common application is seen in facial recognition, image, and text classification.

models.name: Metaverses
models.description: Similar to alternate universes, metaverses are capable of performing different tasks simultaneously. For instance, they can conduct business, establish virtual lives, and generate income. They have a high potential for growth and, hence, are part of recent Machine Learning trends.

models.name: Quantum Computing
models.description: The complex problem needs advanced solutions. Quantum computing is among the current trends in AI that offer solutions and breakthroughs to machine learning algorithms and optimization problems. It addresses intricate challenges by leveraging the principles of quantum mechanics.

models.name: Digital Twins
models.description: It is also a new and interesting offering from AI that is currently on trend. It refers to digital copies of assets present in the real world. Gaining a high amount of popularity in the past few years, businesses and governments have greatly benefited from the concept. It can provide real-time insights while providing the ability to monitor and subsequently optimize the performance of their business. The effects are expected in the prediction of the economic impact of the global crisis, disease progression, and customer behaviors.
